  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">XS0675</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Bitwise-or operator used on a sign-extended operand; consider casting to a smaller unsigned type first</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">The compiler implicitly widened and sign-extended a variable, and then used the resulting value in a bitwise OR operation. This can result in unexpected behavior.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">The following sample generates XS0675:</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Code with box"><text styleclass="Code with box" translate="true">// XS0675.prg  </text><br/><text styleclass="Code with box" translate="true">// compile with: /W:3  </text><br/><text styleclass="Code with box" translate="true">using System;  </text><br/><br/><text styleclass="Code with box" translate="true">public class sign </text><br/><text styleclass="Code with box" translate="true">{  </text><br/><text styleclass="Code with box" translate="true">   public static void Main()  </text><br/><text styleclass="Code with box" translate="true">   {  </text><br/><text styleclass="Code with box" translate="true">      int hi = 1;  </text><br/><text styleclass="Code with box" translate="true">      int lo = 1;  </text><br/><text styleclass="Code with box" translate="true">      long value = (((long)hi) &lt;&lt; 32) | lo;              // XS0675  </text><br/><text styleclass="Code with box" translate="true">      // try the following line instead  </text><br/><text styleclass="Code with box" translate="true">      // long value = (((long)hi) &lt;&lt; 32) | ((uint)lo);   // correct  </text><br/><text styleclass="Code with box" translate="true">   }  </text><br/><text styleclass="Code with box" translate="true">}  </text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
  </body>
